  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3508113/" class="title-link">翻译欠佳</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3508113"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Lei_lei/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u33435116-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Lei_lei/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">xanadu_lei</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-05"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-05 16:55:38</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3508113_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  个人觉得: 选材可以, 翻译值得商榷. 由于本书的内容是由他人从克里希那穆提演讲材料编辑而成, 逻辑上不是很完美. 而翻译倾向于直译的方式, 以至于内容表达上, 不够严谨,  逻辑上, 不够连贯. 

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3508113/#comments">(8回应)</a>
