  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5354572/" class="title-link">克氏的图书翻译上采取直译是最正确的方法</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5354572"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2788428/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2788428-46.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2788428/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">不觉晓</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-03-21"
      class="main-meta">2012-03-21 11:54:47</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5354572_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  克里希那穆提所传递的思想，本身就是非常精妙的，不仅需要读者有精妙的心去理解领悟，更需要传播它的人（译者）精准地去传递它。  如果再在翻译上进行文学性、解读性的装饰，那么读者接收到的信息正可谓“失之毫厘谬以千里”，所以本书的译者坚持直译，而非加入了个人发挥的“...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5354572/#comments">(1回应)</a>
